TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select b.FACILITY_ID AS FACILITY_ID, b.FACILITY_CODE AS FACILITY_CODE, b.SAP_PLANT_CODE AS SAP_PLANT_CODE from V_FACILITY b where rtrim(b.facility_code) is not null and rtrim(upper(b.division_group)) = 'SLSP' and b.facility_id = (select max(facility_id) from v_facility x where x.division_group = b.division_group and x.sap_plant_code = b.sap_plant_code and x.facility_code = b.facility_code)
